headline: SWEP Opens Large Scale Propane Testing Facility
summary: SWEP, part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a world-leading supplier of brazed plate heat exchangers (BPHEs), today announced the opening of a new rig for propane testing at the SWEP Research & Development Center in Landskrona, Sweden.
